{"tid":128313,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Amazon即日起降低免運費門檻","createTime":"2017-02-20T16:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T08:01:01.000Z","uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68c382a88da4cf335f608ef81e0a7fa372d392ec","tid":128313,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:42:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>Amazon即日起降低免運費門檻</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZRW512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZRW512.png&h=5831e3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWalmart早前取消ShippingPass服務來跟Amazon搶客，任何顧客只要買滿美金35元就可享有最快2天免費運送服務。Amazon為回應Walmart的競爭，今天也把免運費門檻由美金49元，同樣降至35元。<br />\n<br />\n以前的ShippingPass，客人需訂閱及付USD49年費，才可享任何消費都可以免運費。Amazon Prime也有類似訂閱服務，但收費每年USD99，不過同時可以擁有Prime Video, Amazon Music等服務。<br />\n<br />\n在2月，Walmart已把ShippingPass服務取消，而之前客人需購物滿50元才免運費，現時客人買滿35元就可以，更吸引的是最快2天送到府上。Amazon有見及此，即日起免運費門檻由消費滿49元，與Walmart一樣，降低至35元。<br />\n<br />\n其實，因為物流成本上漲，Amazon去年「加價」把門檻由35元增至49元。可是，客戶和銷售數字看來對Amazon更重要，蝕本也要留著他們。無論如何，這個網購競爭，對你我的荷包都有好處。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2017/02/19/amazon-lowers-free-shipping-minimum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2Famazon-lowers-free-shipping-minimum%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=de885b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.engadget.com/2017/02/19/amazon-lowers-free-shipping-minimum/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2017/01/31/walmart-kills-its-amazon-prime-style-shipping-service/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2Fwalmart-kills-its-amazon-prime-style-shipping-service%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5ee6d620\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.engadget.com/2017/01/31/walmart-kills-its-amazon-prime-style-shipping-service/</a>"},{"pid":"3aa056e1468b18b51aa869c658f839da70ae00e1","tid":128313,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike"